item.title: FAOSTAT API in R
item.description: Introduction To help improve actual evidence bases, here’s a generic tool that I made to access the FAOSTAT API in R. The APi is undocumented as far as I can see. However, there is an unnecessarily complicated R package, but that doesn’t work. This particular example gets population stats for all counties/regions in the world from 1990 to 2021. But you could use it for anything available on the FAOSTAT website.
